      "path": "audio/narrations/prime-factorization/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.72,
      "size": 27504,
      "text": "给你一个数字，比如六十，你能把它一步步拆开吗？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "prime-factorization",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/prime-factorization/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.8,
      "size": 28800,
      "text": "六十等于十二乘以五，而十二又能拆成四乘三。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "prime-factorization",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/prime-factorization/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.0,
      "size": 31968,
      "text": "一直拆下去，直到不能再拆，我们就完成了质因数分解。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "prime-factorization",
      "section_id": "prime",
      "line_id": "def-1",
      "filename": "prime-def-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/prime-factorization/xiaoxiao/prime-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.14,
      "size": 34272,
      "text": "质数只能被一和它自己整除，比如二、三、五、七。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "prime-factorization",
      "section_id": "prime",
      "line_id": "def-2",
      "filename": "prime-def-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/prime-factorization/xiaoxiao/prime-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.94,
      "size": 30960,
      "text": "它们无法再被拆分，就像搭积木时最基本的那些小块。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "prime-factorization",
      "section_id": "prime",
      "line_id": "def-3",
      "filename": "prime-def-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/prime-factorization/xiaoxiao/prime-def-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.08,
      "size": 33264,
      "text": "任何整数，说到底都是由这些质数积木相乘搭起来的。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "prime-factorization",
      "section_id": "tree",
      "line_id": "tree-1",
      "filename": "tree-tree-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/prime-factorization/xiaoxiao/tree-tree-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.4,
      "size": 22464,
      "text": "我们用一棵分解树来记录拆解的过程。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "prime-factorization",
      "section_id": "tree",
      "line_id": "tree-2",
      "filename": "tree-tree-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/prime-factorization/xiaoxiao/tree-tree-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.73,
      "size": 27648,
      "text": "每次把一个合数拆成两个因子，画出两条分支。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "prime-factorization",
      "section_id": "tree",
      "line_id": "tree-3",
      "filename": "tree-tree-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/prime-factorization/xiaoxiao/tree-tree-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.94,
      "size": 30960,
      "text": "当分支上出现绿色的质数，它就成了不再生长的叶子。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "prime-factorization",
      "section_id": "unique",
      "line_id": "uni-1",
      "filename": "unique-uni-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/prime-factorization/xiaoxiao/unique-uni-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.86,
      "size": 29808,
      "text": "无论你先拆哪一步，最后收集到的质数都完全一样。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "prime-factorization",
      "section_id": "unique",
      "line_id": "uni-2",
      "filename": "unique-uni-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/prime-factorization/xiaoxiao/unique-uni-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.83,
      "size": 29232,
      "text": "六十总是二乘二乘三乘五，这就是算术基本定理。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "prime-factorization",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
